--- Download and installation

1. Download this Bayesian belief networks convertor package from the following url,

http://www.kddresearch.org/KDD/Groups/Probabilistic-Reasoning/convertor.html

The package includes this file, 15 java source files, and 9 test BBN files
all in different formats.

2. Extract it to your disk using "tar xvf convertor.tar" under unix/linux and Winzip under Windows, 
  you get the a directory "convertor" with the following content,

**************************************************************************
